It offers commercial machines, and small restaurant or single customization machines, as well as hypotonic saline and antioxidant ingredient blends. The company provides its products for various applications, such as seafood, shellfish, beef, ground beef, pork, poultry, soy, and produce. It serves supermarkets, restaurants, natural food stores and farmer’s markets, food commissaries and distribution centers, processors and manufacturers, and growers and harvesters. Grovac Systems International, L.C. was founded in 1985 and is based in Rogers, Arkansas.
